response.original_title: Aretha Franklin - Live at the Fillmore West - Quadio Blu-Ray
response.overview: Aretha Franklin played three brilliant nights - March 5, 6, and 7 - at San Francisco’s legendary Fillmore West venue. Between the three nights, Franklin adorned the audience with powerhouse performances of Otis Redding’s “Respect,” Bread’s “Make It With You,” and the Beatles’ “Eleanor Rigby,” earning the record a #1 and #7 spots on Billboard’s Top R&B/Hip-Hop Albums and 200 charts.  Transferred From The Original Half-Inch Four-Channel Masters. Blu-ray With 192/24 Resolution Quadraphonic And Hi-Res Stereo Mixes.
response.title: Aretha Franklin - Live at the Fillmore West - Quadio Blu-Ray
